Sprint 8
Goal: harden release quality and complete lower-priority UX/ops improvements.

Stories:

KNO-903 Article approval/versioning
AUT-1003 Replace placeholder console feed
QLT-1102 API tests for core business rules
QLT-1103 End-to-end smoke tests
Estimated capacity:

24 points
