regression protection added across major domains
knowledge content lifecycle becomes governed
automation UI becomes fully operational
Risks:

testing scope can expand quickly unless tightly prioritized
Priority Summary

Highest business value first:
Sprint 1 to 4
Operational maturity next:
Sprint 5 to 6
Governance and hardening last:
Sprint 7 to 8
Recommended Release Checkpoints

Release A after Sprint 2
agency + commission request baseline
Release B after Sprint 4
finance operations baseline
Release C after Sprint 6
HR docs + integrations + company analytics baseline
Release D after Sprint 8
knowledge, automation, testing hardening